<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: lightgray;
    color: #333;
}

.about-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 50px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.about-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: yellow;
    border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
}

.about-header h1 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #333;
}

.about-content {
    padding: 20px;
}

.about-content h2 {
    color: #333;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.about-content p, .about-content ul {
    margin: 10px 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.about-content ul {
    list-style-type: square;
    padding-left: 20px;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-container">
        <header class="about-header">
            <h1>About Our Blog</h1>
        </header>
        <section class="about-content">
            <p>Welcome to our coding and programming blog! Our goal is to provide insightful articles, tutorials, and resources to help you on your programming journey.</p>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>We strive to empower developers of all skill levels by sharing knowledge and fostering a community of learners and innovators.</p>
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Innovation</li>
                <li>Education</li>
                <li>Community</li>
                <li>Integrity</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
